      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "你这就是抬杠",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "我没有抬杠，我只是有自己的历史观",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "就算是我现在也不觉得你在抬杠，你只是在坚持自己认为的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "算了，换话题吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "下雪的日子不要吵架",
