      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "可我又不是你的学生",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "你不要拿上课那套对我 我不喜欢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "这确实是我的职业病",
