      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "以后别人一跟我聊天，我就马上把我的理念通通抛出来，好吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "【乖巧】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "哦，我忽然想到一件好笑的事情",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你说",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "怎么，还让我请你吗？",
